SUMMARY
================================================================================
Week 1: Arrays/Strings, Hashing, Stacks, Linked Lists
Week 2: Trees (traversals, BST, DP), Tries, Graph BFS/DFS, Union-Find
Week 3: DP (1D, Knapsack, Interval, Grid, Tree DP, Bitmask)
Week 4: Graph shortest paths, Greedy, Heaps, Binary-search-on-answer, Sweep Line, Bits
